data.description: Welcome to your dream home with no HOA, no deed restrictions and almost a full acre of land – an oasis of freedom and space! This stunning, custom-built, 4 BR, 3 BA residence offers a spacious 2,708 sq. ft of luxurious living in a quiet, rural setting just minutes from I-4! This home is designed for those who appreciate quality and style. As you enter, you'll be captivated by the beautiful hardwood flooring in the living areas, giving the space an elegant and warm feel. Ceramic tile in wet areas provides durability and easy maintenance. The heart of this home is the gourmet kitchen, featuring 42" wood cabinets, granite countertops, a spacious center island and stainless steel appliances. The cathedral ceilings in the kitchen and Great Room create a sense of grandeur, while 9'4" ceilings in all other rooms provide an open and spacious feel throughout. With a split bedroom plan, this home offers privacy and convenience for everyone. The spacious 17'x32' screened lanai is the perfect spot to enjoy the serene beauty of your wooded view with no backyard neighbors.  You'll relish the peace and tranquility that this home offers from the front as well - did you notice the koi pond?  Enjoy the sunrise from your front porch while listening to the sounds of the early morning and your private water feature. This property also has a 3-car, side-load garage and is equipped with solar panels (all paid off!) and a solar-powered Tesla® backup battery, ensuring energy efficiency and peace of mind. The backyard storage shed with a custom deck or outdoor entertaining adds even more storage and versatility to your property. Your private well and septic system means no water or sewer bills! This is an exceptional opportunity to own a unique and meticulously maintained property.
